    "explanation": "'She'll prefer to stay home tonight': Lei preferirà restare a casa stasera. Preferire takes -isc- in the present (preferisco) but never in the future: the stem is simply preferir-, giving preferirà. Carrying the insert across (preferiscirà) is the slip to avoid.",
